name: FD
tagline: Floppy Disk Tool for N8VEM Project
body:
### Summary
Application to test the hardware functionality of the Floppy Disk
Controller (FDC) on the ECB DISK I/O, DISK I/O V3, ZETA SBC, 
Dual IDE w/ Floppy, or N8 board.

### Binary Distribution
Pre-built binaries are available at <https://github.com/wwarthen/fd/releases/latest>

### Support or Contact
